import { useState } from "react" import { useEffect } from "react" import { useDispatch, useSelector} from "react-redux" import { getTypes } from "../../Components/Redux/Actions" import axios from "axios" const Form = ()=>{ const dispatch = useDispatch(); const tipos = useSelector((state)=>state.type) const [form, setForm] = useState({ Nombre:"", Imagen:"", Vida:"", Ataque:"", Defensa:"", Velocidad:"", Altura:"", Peso:"", tipo:[] }) useEffect(() => { dispatch(getTypes()) }, [dispatch]) const changeHandler = (event)=>{ const property = event.target.name; const value = event.target.value; setForm({...form,[property]:value}) } const handlerSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault() axios.post("localhost:3001/pokemons",form) .then(res=>alert(res)) } const typeSelect = (e) => { if (form.tipo.length < 2) { setInput({ ...form, tipo: [...form.tipo, e.target.value] }) } } return(
) } export default Form;
